{"tid":826912,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「我該動手術嗎？」TWICE多賢「魅力單眼皮」居然消失...","createTime":"2018-09-18T14:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T18:12:10.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"69f5064a89f4687d48484fefab26774847601894","tid":826912,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"成員多賢在直播中表示：「如果粉絲們願意的話，我會履行之前的貼雙眼皮的約定」，而成員們當然沒有放過這個機會，興奮的幫多賢貼上雙眼皮貼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2018/09/18/550_1311475_1537241394.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F550_1311475_1537241394.webp&h=b5665441&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2018/09/18/550_1311481_1537241446.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F550_1311481_1537241446.webp&h=45ad8683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貼完之後，多賢自己都很不可置信地看著自己的眼睛，不過其他成員們則是一陣讚賞，並說：「還不錯阿！」、「很漂亮欸」讓多賢連忙接問：「那我該去動手術嗎？」ㅋㅋㅋ<br />\n看來多賢也很滿意自己的雙眼皮造型呢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/5f27c02ee36aeb9caa089b6fb46eb118/5C1C348A/t51.2885-15/e35/41704008_323381734881298_97528311157783614_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F5f27c02ee36aeb9caa089b6fb46eb118%2F5C1C348A%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F41704008_323381734881298_97528311157783614_n.jpg&h=77a7e2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而既然都聽好雙眼皮貼了，怎麼能放棄拍幾張美美的照片呢！<br />\n在TWICE的SNS上就可以看到多賢滿意的自拍集阿！<br />\n粉絲們也喜歡雙眼皮的多賢嗎？還是喜歡單眼皮的多賢呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係中2單眼皮既賢寶多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce3a7e95b3c3844e657c99e6d4c2b9975322bbf","tid":826912,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"多賢好正啊啊啊啊啊啊"},{"pid":"29b4f7d88ec93fa845cd7fc3d76086692028dbaa","tid":826912,"uid":42942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:19:58.000Z","